common stakeholders - vote(merger)

stock : ownership of company certificate
share : no of stocks owned
authorized share : type, number - requires authorization to issue large number of shares(issued shares)

outstanding share : not reacquired by company


treasury stock : purchase own stock

stock split
stock dividends

preferred stock : receive dividends before common stock inturn giveup right to share in corp earnings excess in their stated dividends



Book value : 
	
book value of corp : 
	total stockholder's equity - bal sheet
	bal sheet asset - liabilities
	
book value per share of common stock : 
	total equity / outstanding shares
	
if corp has both preferred and common stock - find book value of preferred stock minus from equity



